BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:nFeG9G5HQO4Vi18AuA_2T
SUMMARY:Spelling Bee 2026
DTSTAMP:20260317T051042Z
DTSTART:20260329T130000Z
DESCRIPTION:Want to watch 90 middle-schoolers knock out words like éclairci
	ssement\\\, palooka\\\, and quonk? So do we!  \\nThe regional spelling bee
	 brings together students from schools across King and Snohomish Counties 
	who have already proven themselves to be fantastic spellers. This year’s b
	ee will be moderated by Seattle Radio Theatre founder and KIRO Radio’s pro
	ducer\\\, host\\\, and historian Feliks Banel. The winner will advance to 
	the annual Scripps National Spelling Bee in Washington\\\, D.C. Join us to
	 support our outstanding students as they grapple with high-level language
	 and cheer them on as they try to take the championship in 2026!\n\nhttps:
	//townhallseattle.org/event/spelling-bee-2026/\n\nFrom Town Hall Seattle
URL:https://townhallseattle.org/event/spelling-bee-2026/
LOCATION:The Great Hall\\\, 1119 Eighth Avenue (enter on Eighth Avenue)\\\,
	 Seattle\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:town-hall-seattle
CATEGORIES:Town Hall Seattle
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT
END:VEVENT
